description.narrative:
Overall objective: Contribute to the protection of Afghan citizens from the spread of COVID-19 and to strengthen the national health systems preparedness and capacity to respond to public health emergencies.
Specific objectives: 
1.	Increase the response capacity of the health system;
2.	Improve infection prevention measures and capacities;
3.	Reduce nutritional risks; and
4.	Strengthen and sustain community efforts to prevent the spread of COVID-19 in alignment with the national COVID-19 Global Response Plan, guidelines and strategic priorities.
